==Documentation==
This template creates a full company page layout with hero section, tabs, wiki content, and sidebar.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

The page structure follows the classic Giant Bomb wiki design:
* Hero section with logo/image, title, and deck
* Tab navigation for sub-pages
* Two-column layout with wiki content on left and company details sidebar on right

